title: One Full Year of Taylor Swift (Anniversary Special) (13’s Version)
description:
We are going one year strong and our Queen, Taylor Swift, has made it an interesting one for sure! We reflect on the roller coaster ride that she has taken us on in the last year! Plus, what do we hope for in this upcoming year? There are lots of ways to reach us, and we love hearing from fellow Swifties!
What do you think she's going to do in the next year? What would you like for us to do?
